name: FloridaGatorFacts
0:
”Alexa "open Florida Gator Facts."”
”Alexa "tell me a fact from Florida Gator Facts."”
”Alexa "ask florida gator facts for a fact"”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: florida gator facts
des: The app can be activated by saying "Open Florida Gator Facts", "Tell me a fact from Florida Gator Facts", and more. It can give you one out of nine different facts coded in to the app. The facts are about the coaches and championships.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
